headline: Why Is Halliburton (HAL) Up 4.9% Since Last Earnings Report?
summary: Halliburton (HAL) reported earnings 30 days ago. What's next for the stock? We take a look at earnings estimates for some clues.

headline: Trump And Iran Put Oil Prices Near Six-Month Highs But This Energy Industry Was Already Rallying
summary: President Donald Trump has set the stage for a possible military strike on Iran, presumably to pressure the country to meet demands for a nuclear deal.  The resulting tension between the U.S and Iran sent oil prices near six-month highs  and boosted some oil and gas stocks Thursday.  U.S. oil prices traded less than 1% lower early Friday, holding above $66 per barrel.
